<!-- Style Options -->
<style>
:root {
    /* To hide the hero's dark background, set the value to 0 (default 60% or .6) */
    --hero-background-transparency: 60%;
    
    /* There is also a box shadow.  To remove it, set the value to 0 (default 28% or .28) */
    --hero-box-shadow-transparency: 28%;
    
    /* to have square edges on the background, set the border radius to 0 */
    --hero-border-radius: 10px;
  
    }
    
</style>


<!-- Variables: Change site-wide values such as border radius, font sizes, etc. -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/sfsites/c/resource/SDO_Experience_SiteStyles/css-variables.css" />

<!-- Find page specific styles here -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/sfsites/c/resource/SDO_Experience_SiteStyles/content-pages.css" />

<!-- Styles specific to the header and footer of the site, such as the shadow under the header -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/sfsites/c/resource/SDO_Experience_SiteStyles/header-footer.css" />

<!-- Styles specific to the hero element -->
<!-- To remove the hero, comment out this style -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/sfsites/c/resource/SDO_Experience_SiteStyles/hero.css" />

<!-- Various styles that impact every page of the site -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/sfsites/c/resource/SDO_Experience_SiteStyles/global.css" />


<!-- Font Awesome Free kit -->
<script src="https://demo-studio-cdn.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/fontawesome/fontawesome-free-6.6.0-web/js/all.min.js"></script>



<script>
    window.addEventListener("onEmbeddedMessagingReady", () => {
        console.log ('Received the onEmbeddedMessagingReady event...');
        var userId = $A.get('$SObjectType.CurrentUser.Id');
        console.log ('Passing HiddenPrechatUserId = userId (currently Logged In User Id, or ' + userId + ')');
        embeddedservice_bootstrap.prechatAPI.setHiddenPrechatFields({'HiddenPrechatUserId' : userId});
    });
</script>
